flowchart TB
  EXPLICIT[显式 kind]
  AUTO[自动分类<br/>decision / risk / glossary / unsorted]
  BATCH[结构化批量输入]
  ROUTE[按 kind 路由到文件与 section]

  APPEND[append 型知识<br/>decision / risk / glossary / source / shared-*]
  UPSERT[upsert 型快照<br/>overview / scope / constraint / filemap]
  FALLBACK[待分类与候选<br/>unsorted / pending]

  DEDUP{存在相似 entry?}
  WRITE[写入目标文件]
  REVIEW[读取候选<br/>rewrite / delete / force / skip]
  CROSS{可跨分支复用?}
  STAGE[pending-promotion.md]
  DONE[更新 manifest 与 log]

  EXPLICIT --> ROUTE
  AUTO --> ROUTE
  BATCH --> ROUTE
  ROUTE --> APPEND
  ROUTE --> UPSERT
  ROUTE --> FALLBACK
  APPEND --> DEDUP
  DEDUP -->|否| WRITE
  DEDUP -->|是| REVIEW
  REVIEW --> WRITE
  UPSERT --> WRITE
  FALLBACK --> WRITE
  WRITE --> CROSS
  CROSS -->|是| STAGE
  CROSS -->|否| DONE
  STAGE --> DONE

  classDef input fill:#dbeafe,stroke:#2563eb,color:#172554
  classDef route fill:#ede9fe,stroke:#7c3aed,color:#2e1065
  classDef append fill:#ecfeff,stroke:#0891b2,color:#083344
  classDef snapshot fill:#dcfce7,stroke:#16a34a,color:#052e16
  classDef fallback fill:#fef3c7,stroke:#d97706,color:#451a03
  classDef action fill:#ffffff,stroke:#64748b,color:#0f172a
  classDef stage fill:#f3e8ff,stroke:#9333ea,color:#3b0764
  class EXPLICIT,AUTO,BATCH input
  class ROUTE route
  class APPEND append
  class UPSERT snapshot
  class FALLBACK fallback
  class DEDUP,WRITE,REVIEW,CROSS,DONE action
  class STAGE stage
